1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:12,000
If writing YouTube scripts takes you hours, this workflow cuts the process to about twenty minutes.
Use ChatGPT, Notion AI, and Canva AI to build a full script pack fast.

2
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:28,000
Step one: collect three high-performing videos in your niche.
Extract hook style, pacing, and CTA pattern for context.

3
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:44,000
Step two: prompt ChatGPT for three hook options:
curiosity, contrarian, and authority.

4
00:00:44,000 --> 00:01:00,000
Step three: move the best hook into Notion AI.
Generate a structured outline: hook, value points, proof, CTA.

5
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:16,000
Step four: run a clarity pass in ChatGPT.
Then generate thumbnail concepts in Canva AI.

6
00:01:16,000 --> 00:01:30,000
Result: hook variants, final script, CTA options, and thumbnail text ideas.
Repeat weekly for quality and speed gains.
